{"tid":879131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東話唔撚係中文?","createTime":"2018-10-27T16:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T16:59:32.000Z","uid":128921,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"412824454b5fdd5cad597359f1ba5a005d45f255","tid":879131,"uid":128921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"啲台狗真係on99，自大到，支那人都冇佢地咁自大，講廣東話就叫人講中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6f864d27d33439b628007046ba5875808e1437","tid":879131,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"412824454b5fdd5cad597359f1ba5a005d45f255","tid":879131,"uid":128921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:35:41.000Z","msg":"啲台狗真係on99，自大到，支那人都冇佢地咁自大，講廣東話就叫人講中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"班臺灣人真係覺得中文=國語<br />\n戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後同佢講不如臺灣用返臺語敎中文<br />\n佢就一幅咁嘅表情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 「我覺得這樣很奇怪啦」"},{"pid":"f9c8de058be05a8c8958be9cace49c860098517b","tid":879131,"uid":21849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:40:14.000Z","msg":"垃圾台狗"},{"pid":"fb9d213d05441b658a66fd4f74f0eb3e348a5411","tid":879131,"uid":157827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打機遇到台灣人仲要就佢地講嘢，想講屌都要卡住"},{"pid":"f396078b46db89dd281b374aa5f1d45e441ae438","tid":879131,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:48:20.000Z","msg":"弱智唔識分語文同語言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe218a5d48c9ac5d4bfaf353fee28e48b7367dfb","tid":879131,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/28/005326_34fce6ed1ed3311bad0588ddcf418754.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F28%2F005326_34fce6ed1ed3311bad0588ddcf418754.gif&h=91970611&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6db4203a7e04a91a01d88924fd34c03a7f1a336","tid":879131,"uid":205616,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"廣東話普遍指稱為粵語<br />\n而粵語的確唔係中國語（普通話）<br />\n喺書寫方案入面，粵文係書寫粵語嘅工具<br />\n中文則為書寫現代漢語普通話，亦即中國語嘅工具<br />\n所以某程度上佢係講得冇錯嘅<br />\n下次你見到呢啲台狗<br />\n你可以話「你憑咩老逢要講外國語嘅外國人識你哋啲垃圾中文呀中國人（中華民國（不被國際承認））"}]}